{"tid":364422,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼拍星戰Obi-Wan外傳","createTime":"2017-08-18T11:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T14:33:31.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc8793e2150afb6263c885e8615c5822226ceb63","tid":364422,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"再有《星球大戰》（Star Wars）外傳電影推出！除咗現進行拍攝、以經典角色「漢蘇奴」（Han Solo）少年時代為故事骨幹嘅《Han Solo: A Star Wars Story》之外，美國電影雜誌《The Hollywood Reporter》搶先爆另一套以絕地武士「奧比溫」（Obi-Wan Kenobi ）為中心嘅外傳電影亦正在籌備當中！&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電影現處於早期籌備階段，暫時未有劇本，金像提名導演Stephen Daldry獲斟加盟，如果成事，佢將會跟魯卡斯電影公司（Lucasfilm）合作，負責監督整個籌備拍攝過程。「奧比溫」一角過往曾由男星伊雲麥格高（Ewan McGregor）及已故男星雅歷堅尼斯（Alec Guinness）飾演，雅歷於1977年更憑《星球大戰IV:新的希望》（Star Wars: Episode IV-A New Hope）提名奧斯卡最佳男配角。由於時候尚早，仍未知「奧比溫」一角會由誰人出演，故事的時間背景統統未落實，不過伊雲之前受訪就曾公開表示有意再演「奧比溫」，對角色的延伸故事感興趣，未知會否如願回歸，或電影公司望起用新人擔正。"},{"pid":"d64f7ea67e5bc5814582ce22e1296cbe1a8092ab","tid":364422,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:20:50.000Z","msg":"等咗好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1465deba3a902fbafcca4245a5f4eb1af78437c9","tid":364422,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:40:05.000Z","msg":"用番伊雲就好"},{"pid":"986ec15db64d764f64517bdf8f5427b2652dba43","tid":364422,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"最愛既星戰角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cea849855e11d8f0a7cafacc0e5824c8bdedfe","tid":364422,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"仲有咩好講？前傳正傳都有既角色<br />\n不如講個紫劍黑鬼/obi-wan師傅仲好"},{"pid":"0be9231fa37b04d7fe9d83c190ac8c31a56456c3","tid":364422,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76983870d8edb379a23